Logitech G110 Color Changer

Video can be found here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VZwyxtJMJU

Install Python: http://www.python.org/download/ (I went with v2.7.6)
Install PyUSB: http://sourceforge.net/projects/pyusb/
Install a libUSB driver for the keyboard: http://sourceforge.net/projects/libusb-win32/

Edit the script to make sure you have the right productID. (I am not sure if this changes with each device)

To run: python g110_color_changer.py